      "title": "Facilitating talks with IMF, creditors, my priority -  Foreign Minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign Affairs Minister Ali Sabry said facilitation of talks with the International Monetary Fund ( IMF) and creditors is his priority in the new job .",
        "The Minister told Daily Mirror that he would first take stock of the situation.",
        "\u201cToday, the first priority is to deal with the IMF and the creditors including bond holders,\u201d he said."
      ],
